title: The Psycho TPB (Vertigo)
description:
In order to find out why he was set up, a special operative undergoes a dangerous treatment that may kill him or leave him with superpowers. But will it leave his mind intact? 

Written by James D. Hudnall and with art by Dan Brereton.  The series was originally published as a three-issue prestige series by DC Comics in 1991.  This is a scan of the trade paperback published by Image Comics in 2006.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
